For some reason the chunk maker loops cannot start at 1, so they start at 0.
Making the first chunk ID 0 x 0 even tho it should be 1 x 1 because it is a surface area.
Found out later they can start at 0, it just when testing with 1, I mistakenly forced a 0 by creating a chunk Id manually.

